<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media -- Advertising:
   Isuzu Seems Poised to Select a Small Shop
   ----
   By Thomas R. King
</HL>
<DATE>
07/03/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B3
</SO>
<CO>
   J.DEN J.FJH J.IZM OMC WNEWS
</CO>
